SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1777551071
OL,3,CThe 'forgotten' women waiting years
OL,4,Cfor breast surgery
OL,6,FA woman who has been on the waiting
OL,7,Flist for breast reconstruction surgery
OL,8,Fsince a mastectomy three years ago
OL,9,Fsays she feels "totally forgotten
OL,10,Fabout".
OL,12,FRebecca Joselyn, 43, had to have a
OL,13,Fbreast removed in December 2023 due to
OL,14,Fan aggressive form of cancer.
OL,16,FShe said she was told at the time it
OL,17,Fcould be 12 to 18 months before she
OL,18,Fhad reconstructive surgery.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1777551071
OL,3,CThe 'forgotten' women waiting years
OL,4,Cfor breast surgery
OL,6,FBut the professional silversmith, from
OL,7,FSheffield, has recently discovered she
OL,8,Fmay have to wait until beyond 2027.
OL,10,F"It just feels I'm completely
OL,11,Fforgotten about, that nobody really
OL,12,Fcares," she said.
OL,14,F"I'm not really in the system and I
OL,15,Ffeel like I'm just being told lies."
OL,17,FRebecca was unable to have
OL,18,Freconstructive treatment at the time
OL,19,Fof her mastectomy because
OL,20,Fimmunotherapy had left her too unwell.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1777551071
OL,3,CThe 'forgotten' women waiting years
OL,4,Cfor breast surgery
OL,6,FA month later she was told she had
OL,7,Fbeen added to the waiting list.
OL,9,FShe added: "Twelve to 18 months later,
OL,10,FI started contacting the hospital,
OL,11,Fonly to find out that there was no
OL,12,Frecord of me being added to the wait
OL,13,Flist.
OL,15,F"So I got an appointment, I went to
OL,16,Fsee the surgeon, I broke down. They
OL,17,Fsaid that they would push it through.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1777551071
OL,3,CThe 'forgotten' women waiting years
OL,4,Cfor breast surgery
OL,6,F"I called in December 2025 to find out
OL,7,Fwhere I was and they said I was number
OL,8,Fsix on the waiting list and that it
OL,9,Fwould be six to eight months.
OL,11,F"I phoned this February to be told
OL,12,Fthat it wouldn't be this year and it
OL,13,Fwon't be next year. That would be
OL,14,Fgetting on for four years without even
OL,15,Fan appointment to know how I can move
OL,16,Fforward with this."
OL,18,FShe has been wearing a prosthetic
OL,19,Fbreast while waiting for surgery,
OL,20,Fwhich she said had caused her huge
OL,21,Fdiscomfort.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1777551071
OL,3,CThe 'forgotten' women waiting years
OL,4,Cfor breast surgery
OL,6,FAnd she has had to cancel work because
OL,7,Fof the uncertainty about when she
OL,8,Fmight be called in to hospital.
OL,10,FShe said: "I survive off shows and
OL,11,Fevents, which I travel up and down the
OL,12,Fcountry to do, and I've been waiting
OL,13,Fon different timelines for this
OL,14,Foperation, which is a huge recovery
OL,15,Ftime - it's 12 weeks minimum.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1777551071
OL,3,CThe 'forgotten' women waiting years
OL,4,Cfor breast surgery
OL,6,F"I'm a silversmith so I use machinery
OL,7,Fand tools. And I've not been able to
OL,8,Fpre-book or pre-plan because I'm in
OL,9,Fthis limbo of waiting, you know, so
OL,10,Fit's affecting my livelihood
OL,11,Fmassively."
OL,13,FRebecca is one of several breast
OL,14,Fcancer patients in Sheffield facing
OL,15,Flong waits for surgery.
OL,17,FNicola Lovell, who wanted a double
OL,18,Fmastectomy due to a family history of
OL,19,Fcancer, resorted to paying #15,000 to
OL,20,Fhave a private operation in 2023 after
OL,21,Fwaiting years for NHS surgery.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1777551071
OL,3,CThe 'forgotten' women waiting years
OL,4,Cfor breast surgery
OL,6,F"I couldn't wait any longer and I do
OL,7,Fbelieve that had I not had my family
OL,8,Fnot put that money together I probably
OL,9,Fwouldn't be here to tell you this tale
OL,10,Ftoday," she said.
OL,12,FAfter another two-year wait she had
OL,13,Freconstructive surgery, but says her
OL,14,Fdaughter is now stuck in the same
OL,15,Fcycle waiting for treatment.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1777551071
OL,3,CThe 'forgotten' women waiting years
OL,4,Cfor breast surgery
OL,6,F"It's been a year since she saw the
OL,7,Fsurgeon. Again, no communication, and
OL,8,Fyou're constantly battling. You're
OL,9,Fconstantly having to pick up that
OL,10,Fphone, go from one department to
OL,11,Fanother.
OL,13,F"There's no, 'we're really sorry that
OL,14,Fyou're waiting', nobody getting in
OL,15,Ftouch with you, letting you know
OL,16,Fwhat's happening... it's very
OL,17,Ftraumatic."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1777551071
OL,3,CThe 'forgotten' women waiting years
OL,4,Cfor breast surgery
OL,6,FTracy Watson had a preventative
OL,7,Fmastectomy in January 2023. She had
OL,8,Fsurgery to reconstruct her breast
OL,9,Fshortly afterwards, but now campaigns
OL,10,Ffor other women not afforded the same
OL,11,Ftimely treatment.
OL,13,FShe said: "It's shocking. The trust,
OL,14,Fwho can't be trusted, need to be
OL,15,Fashamed of themselves.
OL,17,F"There are solutions, there are ways
OL,18,Fforward. If you look at London,
OL,19,Fthey've done a blitz on the backlog
OL,20,Fand they cleared three months' waiting
OL,21,Flist within five days. It can be done.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1777551071
OL,3,CThe 'forgotten' women waiting years
OL,4,Cfor breast surgery
OL,6,F"Here in South Yorkshire, we've got
OL,7,FPinderfields, 45 minutes away. Their
OL,8,Fwaiting list is a year, but yet in
OL,9,FSheffield, it's three years plus. So
OL,10,Fthere's no equality in this... I won't
OL,11,Fgo away until this problem goes away."
OL,13,FJane McNicholas, chief medical officer
OL,14,Fat Sheffield Teaching Hospitals NHS
OL,15,FFoundation Trust, apologised for the
OL,16,F"frustration and distress" caused to
OL,17,Fwomen like Rebecca facing long waits
OL,18,Ffor surgery.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1777551071
OL,3,CThe 'forgotten' women waiting years
OL,4,Cfor breast surgery
OL,6,FShe added: "The demand for this type
OL,7,Fof reconstruction has increased
OL,8,Fsignificantly in recent years and this
OL,9,Fis now exceeding the capacity
OL,10,Favailable.
OL,12,F"The situation is further compounded
OL,13,Fby the complexity of the procedure
OL,14,Fwhich requires multiple surgeons and
OL,15,Fscrub teams along with an extended
OL,16,Foperating day for a single case."
OL,18,FShe added that other NHS centres faced
OL,19,Fthe same challenge "so options to be
OL,20,Ftreated elsewhere are also limited".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1777551071
OL,3,CThe 'forgotten' women waiting years
OL,4,Cfor breast surgery
OL,6,FMs McNichols added: "We are recruiting
OL,7,Fadditional surgeons but there is a
OL,8,Flimited supply of specialists who can
OL,9,Fundertake this procedure.
OL,11,F"We increased capacity last year which
OL,12,Fdoubled the number of procedures
OL,13,Fundertaken to 60. Patients have the
OL,14,Foption of alternative forms of
OL,15,Freconstruction, but we appreciate that
OL,16,Fthis is a personal choice and may not
OL,17,Fbe a preferred option.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G12/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1777551071
OL,3,CThe 'forgotten' women waiting years
OL,4,Cfor breast surgery
OL,6,F"We are contacting existing patients
OL,7,Fto update them on the options
OL,8,Favailable given this issue is not
OL,9,Flikely to be resolved in the short
OL,10,Fterm... We apologise for the concern
OL,11,Fthis situation is causing and
OL,12,Freiterate the urgency we are applying
OL,13,Fto this by exploring every opportunity
OL,14,Fto improve the position as quickly as
OL,15,Fpossible."
OL,26,@wD@JO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G13/14
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
